<div class='message-box group' style='text-align: left; width: 500px;'>
  <h2>Code for "<%- form.get('name') %>"</h2>
  <p>Would you like to get the HTML for the code and use it yourself, or would you like us to host the form for you?</p>

  <br>

  <p>Either way, when someone submits the form the results will be posted to your account here at Form-itable.com and your users will be redirected to the url you assigned for this form.</p>

  <br>

  <span class="hosting-choice">
    <span
      class="radio-option"
      style="display: block;">

      <input
       type="radio"
       id="host-option0"
       class="host-option"
       name="host-option"
       value="code">

      <label for="host-option0">
        Give me the code for the form, I will host it myself
      </label>
    </span>

    <span
      class="radio-option"
      style="display: block;">

      <input
        type="radio"
        id="host-option1"
        class="host-option"
       name="host-option"
        value="link">

      <label
        for="host-option1">
        I want to host the form on Form-itable.com, just give me the link
      </label>
    </span>
  </span>

  <br>

  <span class='link-info' style='display: none;'>
    <label>
      Here is the url that will link to your form:
      <br>
      <input
        type='text'
        onClick="$(this).select()"
        size='80'
        readonly
        value="http://form-itable.com/forms/<%- form.get('id') %>">
    </label>
    <br>
    <br>
    <label>
      Here is the html for a link redirect to your form:
      <br>
      <input
        type='text'
        onClick="$(this).select()"
        size='80'
        id='link-code'
        readonly
        value="<a href=<%- 'http://' + document.location.host + '/forms/' +
          form.get('id') %>><%- form.get('name') %></a>">
    </label>

    <br>
    <br>

    <p>Here is what the link will look like, you can click on it to see what your users will see:</p>

    <br>

    <iframe
      style='width: 500px; height: 50px; background-color: white;'>
    </iframe>

  </span>
</div>